  • Adhidarshak Chaturvedi
    Ye bjp ke Shukracharya hain ,Doordarshan par inhe ek ghante ka slot
    de rakha hai yog ,aayurved ko
    rashtrvad, desh bhakti
    hindutv ki sugarcoat
    chadha kar bechte hain,aarysamaji hote
    to bjp ke paas na fatkte ,suna hai kuch
    samay tak gurukul se
    Judav raha hai .
    Paisa adhik ho gaya hai ,inhe baba kahna
    galat hai,lala RamDeo
    Salwar vale kahen to
    Saty ke nikat hoga .
    Kaam vyapar aur tax
    bachane ke liye trust
    banana kya siddh karta hai ? Yah to Dabur ,Vaidynath , sharmayu ,aadi bhi
    Kar sakte the .jahir
    hai ki sar pe sarkar
    ka hath hai .saval hai ki jab vidvat parishad
    hi kabhi kisi ko Rajarshi ka khitab degi
    Kisi ko ghar ghar panhuchayegi to kya
    hoga ?
    Pahli sarkar ne vaidik
    mantrochchar ,shankh
    dhvani ke madhy shapath grahan kiya tha,aur Gandhi parivar
    Ki Jaden khodne ka
    Sankalp lene valon ki
    Vajah se apne desh ,
    Apni Dharti par paanch
    lakh Brahman visthapit
    hain tees saal se ?
    Uttar bharat ke Brahman vidvan aatm
    kendrit na hote to Asaram,Ram Rahim ,
    Ram Pal , Sakshi maharaj , Ram deo
    Jaise lampat dharm
    Ke naam par paon
    nahin pujva sakte the .
